commit.title: [ci] [gitlab] Add tags for fast runner selection + increases parallelism.
commit.message:
[ci] [gitlab] Add tags for fast runner selection + increases parallelism.

- We do the build stage with -j4 + `fast-runner`.
- Most expensive jobs use now `fast-runner`, so failure due to slow
  Gitlab runners is minimized.
